HYMBY = Host In My BackYard
HYMBY = Host Your Mini Blog Yourself

Use Python instead of Lua to do this interface more easily.

For an example:

 * Use Pypy as Python interpreter
 * Use Tornado as python Web Server
 * Use bottle.py as web framework (with bottle.run(server='tornado')
 * Use four thread in nginx on tornado to give a good response

Cf. http://casbon.me/what-will-pypy-do-for-your-website-benchmarki for benchmarking results.

# Similar tools

  * https://projects.gnome.org/gnome-blog/
